metadata.name: Rainbow Drawing G001 Red
metadata.description:
We are always freely moving between the real life and the imaginary world of freedom.
This project is a self-expression that expresses the process of unconsciously exploring and dreaming of life in order to achieve the purpose of life, and the freedom of expression to live life in one's own way in the real world through illustrations of the surreal harmony of fashion and nature.
  This is Girl 001 Red, one of a series of fashion illustrations made in 7 colors.
